Class InSlotListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • irioUtils.InSlotListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.instantreality.InstantIO.InSlot.Listener

    public class InSlotListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.instantreality.InstantIO.InSlot.Listener
    This class implements the actual listener for incoming data from an InstantIO network. The overridden method newData contains the behavior for new data. Incoming data will be transformed into a TTE object and pushed to the queue.
